00:05:19.340 --> 00:05:21.660
Huang Guifen, stop causing trouble here!

00:05:23.370 --> 00:05:24.540
Over there.

00:05:27.250 --> 00:05:28.250
Stop fighting! Stop!

00:05:29.490 --> 00:05:30.580
Here, this way!

00:05:31.250 --> 00:05:32.540
Excuse me.

00:05:33.022 --> 00:05:33.730
Stop fighting!

00:05:33.730 --> 00:05:34.490
Mom!

00:05:34.490 --> 00:05:35.330
Stop fighting!

00:05:35.490 --> 00:05:36.370
Stop it, Mom!

00:05:37.140 --> 00:05:38.290
So you've brought backup too?

00:05:38.290 --> 00:05:38.930
Stop it!

00:05:38.930 --> 00:05:39.770
Guifen!

00:05:42.370 --> 00:05:43.900
