00:05:50.460 --> 00:05:51.660
and you join in, do you?

00:05:51.660 --> 00:05:53.610
Do you even know what's right or wrong?

00:05:53.610 --> 00:05:55.730
Even if others don't know Sibei, you do!

00:05:55.730 --> 00:05:57.580
