00:06:13.050 --> 00:06:13.850
And now you...

00:06:13.850 --> 00:06:15.490
- Have you no conscience left?
- Mom!

00:06:15.980 --> 00:06:17.140
Do you have any shame at all?

00:06:17.340 --> 00:06:19.100
Look at the mess
you've made of my stall!

00:06:19.100 --> 00:06:20.239
