00:06:20.240 --> 00:06:21.410
Fine, how much? I'll pay you!

00:06:21.410 --> 00:06:22.290
At least five hundred!

00:06:22.290 --> 00:06:23.850
Money's all you care about, isn't it?

00:06:29.810 --> 00:06:30.650
Here!

00:06:35.220 --> 00:06:36.060
Mom.

00:06:37.100 --> 00:06:37.940
Move aside.

00:06:39.930 --> 00:06:41.088
Li Mingyu, listen to me.

00:06:42.020 --> 00:06:43.020
My daughter

00:06:43.700 --> 00:06:44.540
has been wronged.

00:06:45.250 --> 00:06:46.660
We'll keep appealing.

00:06:47.700 --> 00:06:50.290
